      "comment": "DREAMERS NEVER DIE (2) wasn't far away fresh before a 3.9L defeat most recently over 1300m. Back to 1100m looks a good move having placed 2/3 at this trip previously and the inside draw should suit. Faithfull hops on board now and he can fire third-up into the campaign. LAVISH CHARM (1) jumped a $1.20 fave here two back before a 2.8L defeat most recently when up to 1200m. He's unbeaten at this course and distance and now third-up into the campaign he makes plenty of appeal. Can find the front and will be very hard to run down. HIGH PRECISION (4) comes back to 1100m today after closing very strongly over 1200m last time out. A better draw this time around suits and she won't be far away. DUBLIN RED (7) is better than she's shown his past couple and can bounce back. PRETTY DEVINE (5) gets the blinkers back on today and should appreciate this easier race.",
